ption";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:227:"WPMU Author Description lets users specify a unique autor description for each individual site in a network. <a href="http://en.wp.obenland.it/wpmu-author-description/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:19:"Konstantin Obenland";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:821:"<p>This plugin lets users specify a unique autor description for each individual site in a network. It falls back to the description of the primary site when no specific description is set.<span id="more-451"></span></p>\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Download <a title="WPMU Author Description in the WordPress Plugin Repository" href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/wpmu-author-description/" target="_blank">WPMU Author Description</a>.</li>\n<li>Unzip the folder into the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<p>None asked yet.</p>\n<h2>Changelog</h2>\n<h3>1.0.1</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed an error when no custom bio was set</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>1.0.0</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial Release</li>\n</ul>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:54:"http://en.wp.obenland.it/wpmu-author-description/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s: